reviews.text: Ramen is ok, soup is good, have to tell the cook for a softer ramen for better taste; but tea is bad. Can be better.

每次行來都要食碗滿足一下。
地道館既車仔麵，不單止地道，更真正是老味道。
豬腸係一舊舊唔係一粒粒，有肉地既雞尖，咖哩尤魚…
回到童年時既口味～
完勝大河道車仔麵！

喺葵涌廣場真係有好多食肆，但係對呢一間麵店都有特別嘅喜好，一般人都會覺得呢間麵店好奇怪，可能會唔夠膽走入去，衛生情況又好似一般，但係呢一間麵店係充滿人情味，因為當你光顧幾次之後，店員就已經記得你曾經食過啲乜嘢，會問你係咪照舊，亦都會親切噓寒問暖。
。
食物方面佢哋嘅車仔麵真係好值得一試，不過個人更加鍾意佢哋嘅麻辣湯底，分左大中小辣，真係惹味，特別係佢哋嘅大腸同埋腩肉，啲大腸洗得好乾淨，亦都好入味，所以特別推介。
。
今日嚟到麵軒，店員就推介我哋食一款餐牌冇嘅特別出品， ＄53 ,咁神秘就梗係要試吓啦，黎到嘅時候覺得好有趣， 海鮮湯底配通心粉，一邊仲有新鮮蝦，扎肉，貢丸，花膠都有，最特別係有一隻新鮮嘅蟶子，蟶子都幾大隻，上面仲有蒜蓉同葱，肉質鮮甜爽口，好好味。
不過店員話呢一個特別嘅出品，唔係日日都有，所以想試嘅話，真係要碰吓運氣啦。
。 
特別要讚呢一間店舖嘅飲品，一定要試佢哋嘅果汁，加＄3就有一杯最鍾意飲鮮橙加香蕉，無添加,鮮榨好鮮甜,好好味嘅一款飲品。
咖哩魷魚好食

result.formatted_address: 11號 Kwai Foo Rd, Kwai Chung, Hong Kong
result.name: Kwai Chung Plaza

reviews.text: A very popular spot for youngsters to go mainly due to its variety of foods, affordable clothes and the random goodies that you can find in certain stores. Cleanliness is not the best because spilled foods can often to be found l on the floor. Can get quite crowded in the afternoon as students would usually come for a snack when school ends.

For a foreigner like me, I felt really lucky to have discovered this place as it was close to our hotel. It has restaurants, an atm machine, and grocery stores where one can get basic necessities. It also has a walkway attached to Kwai Fong station!

A local mall that is full of small eateries and food shops for you to try. I really enjoy going around and just sampling all the food that they have and some are seriously delicious and cheap.

Although the mall mainly has fashion items for females and electronics stuff, I can tell they are of inferior quality and which some you can find online for even cheaper price.

I would suggest to come for the food instead.
lots of old fashioned type individuals small high street store
The good ole gathering place for small, unchained stores
